{"url": "https://www.dofus.com/en/mmorpg/encyclopedia/resources/15181-hairsh-golden-ball", "id": 15181, "name": "Hairsh Golden Ball", "img": "http://staticns.ankama.com/dofus/www/game/items/200/15880.png", "type": "Precious stone", "level": 200, "description": "These balls come in all different colours and glow in the dark. The Hairshes use them to feign magical attacks, which, paired with an icy glare, is enough to send some adventurers running. When not fighting sissies, this bluff technique just makes the Hairshes look even more ridiculous."}